  "detailed_description": "Liquivid Video Merge is an easy-to-use app that allows you to combine multiple video clips into a single one. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nFor each input video, you can select which part of the clip to export and you can optionally choose a music soundtrack for the output file. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe app imports all common video formats and codecs in any resolution (including HD, 2K, 4K).<br />\r\nExports videos as MP4 files with H.264 codec.",
  "about_the_game": "Liquivid Video Merge is an easy-to-use app that allows you to combine multiple video clips into a single one. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nFor each input video, you can select which part of the clip to export and you can optionally choose a music soundtrack for the output file. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe app imports all common video formats and codecs in any resolution (including HD, 2K, 4K).<br />\r\nExports videos as MP4 files with H.264 codec.",
